  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nOur lodestar unit tests are not runnable, they spawn many zombie heavy processes including BeaconNode-s in the background causing OOM or crashing the computer directly.\r\n\r\nSince we are progressively changing from a pattern of constructor does nothing, instance.start() does everything, to constructor initializing background tasks, `sinon.createStubInstance()` will start the classes.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nUnit tests should not pollute environment\r\n\r\n**Steps to Reproduce**\r\n\r\n```\r\ncd packages/lodestar\r\nyarn test:unit\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
